    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 1st level, you gain <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/diplomacy\">Diplomacy</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/knowledge\">Knowledge</a>&nbsp;(history),&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/knowledge\">Knowledge</a>&nbsp;(local),&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/knowledge\">Knowledge</a>&nbsp;(nobility), and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/linguistics\">Linguistics</a>&nbsp;as class skills. In addition, when using these skills to learn, study, or gather information about humans, you add an&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/glossary#TOC-Insight-Bonus\">insight bonus</a>&nbsp;equal to your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Charisma-Cha-\">Charisma</a>&nbsp;bonus on such checks.</p>"
